'''second person'''

#The form of a [[verb]] used (in English and other languages) with the pronouns ''[[thou]]'' and ''[[you]]'' (or their equivalents in other languages). In many languages the singular, applying to one person, and plural, applying to several people, are distinct.
#:''"Are" is the second person of "to be"''
#:''"amas" is the second person singular of the [[Spanish]] verb "amar"''
#:''"amais" is the second person plural of the [[Spanish]] verb "amar"''
